le world together,\\\" said James.\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 673, \"end\": 686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9995321684549174, \"rank\": 0.0002474016381956136, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 0.9999986817860693, \"rank\": 1.1885346942154079e-06, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For a kid from Akron, this responsibility means everything to not only myself, but to my family, all the kids in my hometown, my teammates, fellow Olympians and so many people across the country with big aspirations,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 1013, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 803, \"end\": 808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akron_Zips_football\", \"score\": 0.5479321862133414, \"rank\": 0.7765994619205611, \"text\": \"Akron\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akron_Zips_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akron_Zips_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sports have the power to bring us all together, and I am proud to be a part of this important moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2004, James was on the U.S. Olympic team in Greece.\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 0.9999986817860693, \"rank\": 1.1885346942154079e-06, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q2